    <body>
      <div xml:id="NA384-kiḷavi">
        <p type="edition">iḵtu uṭaṉpōkāniṉṟāṉ malintu taṉṉeñciṟkuc colliyatu.</p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en">This is what is said in joy by the one who was eloping [with her].</p>
        </div>
      <div xml:id="NA384">
        <lg type="edition">
<l>            paṇpuṟap puṟaviṉ ceṅkāṟ cēval</l>
<l>            kaḷari yōṅkiya kavaimuṭ kaḷḷi</l>
<l>            muḷariyaṅ kuṭampaiyi ṉīṉṟiḷaip paṭṭa</l>
<l>            vuyavunaṭaip pēṭai yuṇīiya maṉṉar</l>
<l>            muṉaikavar mutupā ḻukuneṟ peṟūu</l>
<l>            māṇil cēynāṭ ṭatariṭai malarnta</l>
<l>            naṉṉāḷ vēṅkaip poṉmaruḷ putuppū</l>
<l>            parantaṉa naṭakkayāṅ kaṇṭaṉa mātō</l>
<l>            kāṇiṉi vāḻiye ṉeñcē nāṇviṭ</l>
<l>            ṭaruntuya ruḻanta kālai</l>
<l>            marunteṉap paṭūu maṭavō ḷaiyē.</l>
            </lg>
        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>            Didn’t we see [her] while walking over the gold-like</l>
<l rend="indent">            new blossoms that had spread<note place="foot"><term xml:lang="ta">parantaṉa</term>: what to do - read an unmarked sentence end or a <term xml:lang="ta">muṟṟeccam</term>?</note> from the Vēṅkai tree on a good day</l>
<l rend="indent">            that blossomed in the middle of the road to infamous(?) distant lands,</l>
<l rend="indent2">            where the red-legged cock of the beautiful(?) dove</l>
<l rend="indent2">            obtains the paddy that was shed from the old waste, seized by the front</l>
<l rend="indent3">            of the king, for [its] female with suffering gait to eat,</l>
<l rend="indent3">            that was exhausted after giving birth in the nest of thorny twigs</l>
<l rend="indent4">            in the Kaḷḷi tree with forked thorns grown high in the saline soil?</l>
<l>        See now, live, my heart:</l>
<l>        the inexperienced one who is called “remedy”,</l>
<l rend="indent">            at a time she bore difficult suffering,</l>
<l rend="indent2">            shame quitting [her].</l>
        </lg>
      </div>
    </body>
